66931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"2cd5f384247982ca38cbed344ffd8c1193789cc4","tid":1667254,"uid":276989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"蓮藕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390e28427947e2cf6482c934307597d6aa6f454a","tid":1667254,"uid":34828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"用pepe得喇掛"},{"pid":"49c89bf026743ebbc8c7ed62d937abb2506b678b","tid":1667254,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390e28427947e2cf6482c934307597d6aa6f454a","tid":1667254,"uid":34828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"用pepe得喇掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"青蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca378e512bb01d61803fc7d4054831bf4a6a41fa","tid":1667254,"uid":34828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49c89bf026743ebbc8c7ed62d937abb2506b678b","tid":1667254,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390e28427947e2cf6482c934307597d6aa6f454a","tid":1667254,"uid":34828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"用pepe得喇掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:10:32.000Z","msg":"青蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而猛禽，猛獸，或雜食家畜及部分兩棲類（如青蛙）或爬蟲類（如龜、鱉）也是不可食用的。"},{"pid":"92ed03875d0a0157363e9aeced03a0749a765714","tid":1667254,"